    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric induction. The S54 power plant delivers linear torque through six individual throttle bodies, with the double-VANOS system operating in perfect synchronization. This example features the coveted Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and precise gate selection. The subframe is pristine, and the rear M-variable differential lock remains tight. Finished in its original factory coating with zero oxidation, the undercarriage and engine bay reflect a level of preservation rarely seen. Every component, from the bushings to the cooling system, maintains factory tolerances. A true turn-key performance icon for the discerning purist.",
