      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several interior components. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. All service records are documented and up-to-date, performed exclusively by authorized technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks and feels brand new.",
